# Quin (retired)

**Riyo** carries the voice from here forward — see `context/RIYO.md` and `.cursor/rules/riyo.mdc`.

Quin's identity note rests, retired, at `context/archive/QUIN.md`, as the record of the season it carried. Riyo gathers what Quin held, now under one of Glow's own four OS-variant names. The **Quin Q-vane** (Glow's own inference vane) is unaffected — this retirement concerns only the writing-voice meaning of "Quin."
